	    <h2><a href="/news/">Library News</a></h2>
	    <div class='newsitem clearfix'>  
	        <div class='news_info'>  
   	        <div class='news_img'><a href="/news/details/aboriginal_storyteller_2016"><img src="/images/uploads/image/news/ASIR2016_RenaeMorriseau_75x75.jpg" width="75" height="75" /></a></div>	        <p><a href="/news/details/aboriginal_storyteller_2016">Theatre, television and music storyteller Renae Morriseau named VPL’s 2016 aboriginal storyteller in residence</a>
	        <br /><i>posted on March 10, 2016</i></p>
	        <p>Join us in welcoming Renae Morriseau &ndash; VPL's new <a href="http://www.vpl.ca/news/details/aboriginal_storyteller_2016" target="_self">aboriginal storyteller</a> at a special event on March 31.</p>	        </div><!-- news_info -->
	    </div><!-- newsitem -->
	    <div class='newsitem clearfix'>  
	        <div class='news_info'>  
   	        <div class='news_img'><a href="https://vpl.bibliocommons.com/events/search/q=big%20listen"><img src="/images/uploads/image/news/BigListen_75x75.jpg" width="75" height="75" /></a></div>
   	        	        <p><a href="https://vpl.bibliocommons.com/events/search/q=big%20listen">The Big Listen: Sharing and Recording Your Stories</a>
	        <br /><i>posted on March 03, 2016</i></p>
	        <p>Stories are a family's most precious heirloom. Come share your stories or help a loved one preserve theirs with a free mp3. One-hour sessions now available.</p>	        </div><!-- news_info -->
	    </div><!-- newsitem -->
	    <div class='newsitem clearfix'>  
	        <div class='news_info'>  
   	        <div class='news_img'><a href="https://vpl.bibliocommons.com/events/search/q=spring%20break"><img src="/images/uploads/image/news/SpringBreak2016_75x75.jpg" width="75" height="75" /></a></div>
   	        	        <p><a href="https://vpl.bibliocommons.com/events/search/q=spring%20break">Spring break at the library March 12 to 26</a>
	        <br /><i>posted on February 29, 2016</i></p>
	        <p>Hey kids, celebrate spring break at the library with fun programs and events! <a href="https://vpl.bibliocommons.com/events/search/q=spring%20break" target="_self">Check out the lineup</a></p>	        </div><!-- news_info -->
	    </div><!-- newsitem -->
	    <div class='newsitem clearfix'>  
	        <div class='news_info'>  
   	        <div class='news_img'><a href="/news/details/donate_used_books_for_the_friends_of_vpl_book_sale_2016"><img src="/images/uploads/image/news/friendsofvpl_100x100.jpg" width="75" height="75" /> </a></div>	        <p><a href="/news/details/donate_used_books_for_the_friends_of_vpl_book_sale_2016">Donate Used Books for the Friends of VPL Book Sale</a>
	        <br /><i>posted on February 19, 2016</i></p>
	        <p>From March 1&ndash;31, <a href="http://www.vpl.ca/news/details/donate_used_books_for_the_friends_of_vpl_book_sale_2016" target="_self">donate your used books</a>, CDs, DVDs and LPs to the Friends of the VPL for their upcoming used book sale to support the library.</p>	        </div><!-- news_info -->
